ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectOrder Amending the CCRFTA Sugar Aggregate Quantity Limit Order
PrecisORDER AMENDING THE CCRFTA SUGAR AGGREGATE QUANTITY LIMIT ORDER to adjust the numbering of some tariff items in Section 1 of the CCRFTA Sugar Aggregate Quantity Limit Order, which sets out annual quantities of sugar imported from Costa Rica that can benefit from the CCRFTA, with the coming into force of the Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA).
